        "description": {
            "value": "<p><strong>Trigger</strong> An ally attempts a Diplomacy or Intimidation check to [[/act coerce]] or [[/act make-an-impression]].</p><hr /><p>Brenneri ambassadors refer to alternating tones in negotiations as soft paw, sharp claw. If the triggering check is a Diplomacy check, you attempt an Intimidation check, and vice versa. Your ally uses the higher of the two results for their triggering check.</p>"
